{"tid":312853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山窿私樓】港產片再見王老五145呎愛巢 樓價變318萬","createTime":"2017-07-07T20:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T07:35:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f682bceb17810ed2b730a3cfee8b255a4861334","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T20:20:18.000Z","msg":"【山窿私樓】港產片145呎無廚房愛巢 樓價22萬變318萬<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499349426_a110.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499349426_a110.jpg&h=dbe41af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即時財經  2017-07-07 00:00:44 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n樓市狂潮下成家立室，婚後到底租樓等跌好、還是頂硬上入市是每對新人避無可避的兩難選擇題。決志上車而又無父幹的一群，首期掹掹緊、自不然想搵四球內單位、做盡九成按揭，但走盡全城代理舖卻只會發現市區選擇只得納米樓。他們行入單位參選時，或者都會好似電影《再見王老五》中的飾演準新人張曼玉及鍾鎮濤(阿B)咁，響納米樓中心呼喊「哇！乜咁細嫁！」<br />\n<br />\n電影其中一段，曼玉、阿B同地產代理「縮水劉」參觀一個市區單位，客廳窄到伸唔直雙手、睡房淨係夠擺一張床似山窿，隨住去年屯門菁雋公佈最細單位得128方呎，令到電影片段事隔28年後在網絡瘋傳，揶揄納米樓始終如一、發展商賺到盡心態不變。<br />\n<br />\n本報曾向橙天嘉禾及導演爾冬陞求證片段拍攝所在地，前者回覆無法確認，後者也稱已經記不起。其後成功聯絡到其中一位劇組成員憶述，電影該部份是在灣仔軒尼詩道的單幢樓宇拍攝，而區內代理更言之鑿鑿該處是灣仔康富大廈，單位實用面積劃一145方呎，屬全灣仔最細私樓。<br />\n<br />\n對照康富大廈單位圖則與電影取景角度吻合，例如高度及腰的窗台。本報記者早前實地參觀一個同類單位亦能夠重現多個經典場景，但物業入伙已32年，業主已因應情況重新裝修，部份位置有輕微改動。<br />\n<br />\n例如電影中連洗衣機、雪櫃都擺唔落的蚊型明火廚房，被曼玉吐糟「咁細，我點煮飯呀？」，今日已經裝修到變「洗手間」，即只有一個洗手盆的空間，換言之，單位內再無獨立煮食的位置。<br />\n<br />\n電影裡頭地產代理大力推祟的微型電器傢俱，到今日仍然被採用，例如酒店式迷李雪櫃、「享受二人世界」的隱蔽式餐櫃。<br />\n<br />\n至於細到淨喺得一張雙人床嘅睡房，搞到阿B跌落床大嗌「點解會咁嫁！」、曼玉鬧爆「一入房就上床，成個山窿咁！」。去到今日，大部份業主都拆睡房門將單位變開放式。現場度呎，山窿位的確好似電影中「縮水劉」咁講，啱啱擺到張4乘6標準雙人床，想偷些少位做其他用途都無。<br />\n<br />\n最後，劇中花灑對正馬桶的浴室，如今分隔返馬桶同淋浴間，避免出現沖涼花灑直接噴水落馬桶的情況，不過BMI爆標的肥人都相信幾難搞。<br />\n<br />\n康富大康放盤稀少，消息指，最新一宗成交是中層B室，實用面積145方呎，業主企硬叫價318萬元，放盤半個月，最終上月零議價下易手，呎價2.19萬元。區內地產表示，同類型單位市值租金介乎9,000元到1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n據土地註冊處資料顯示，康富大康42伙住宅單位的一手成交全部錄於1985年，成交價介乎20.2萬元到24.2萬元，中層戶成交價約22萬元。<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳東陽 余曉芸 <br />\n攝影：李潤芳 何頴賢<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0511a3dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電影中鍾鎮濤在縮水樓客飯廳無法伸直雙手。( 電影《再見王老五》截圖)<br />\n<br />\n本報記者早前參觀同類單位亦只能勉強伸直雙手。(何頴賢攝)<br />\n<br />\n電影中的縮水樓廚房只能剛剛好容納一個人企立，連廚具都無位擺。 ( 電影《再見王老五》截圖)<br />\n<br />\n本報記者早前參觀同類單位業主直接放棄煮食，將該處改裝成一個洗手盆。 (何頴賢攝)<br />\n<br />\n張曼玉鬧爆「一入房就上床，成個山窿咁！」 ( 電影《再見王老五》截圖)<br />\n<br />\n該處如電影對白所拍，只有4呎乘6呎 (何頴賢攝)<br />\n<br />\n縮水樓中褶合式餐桌必不可少，配酒店式雪櫃如同電影中設計。 (何頴賢攝)"},{"pid":"d5a9b50bfc72f7ca942b9ba97161f5eccedd3e01","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T20:20:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170707&amp;guid=56923646&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170707%26guid%3D56923646%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=69fbae5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170707%26guid%3D56923646%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=34fcbdee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170707&amp;guid=56923646&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"0311f67390e271dcf32da1d65d332edefbcff8f2","tid":312853,"uid":56729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T20:41:59.000Z","msg":"當年睇係笑片<br />\n宜家睇就係documentary"},{"pid":"9382ed89add611fc98cc53f786ca5c1c49c5b355","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T20:45:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SYjWRfqGhm0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSYjWRfqGhm0&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=440fd432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SYjWRfqGhm0</a>"},{"pid":"ae4f08baedb961a59ed9c33ec55f09a1df39821b","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T20:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m1dhVZSL72s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm1dhVZSL72s&d=xWuwrdy%2BTp%2FhwWFpPqP6CSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f94567e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m1dhVZSL72s</a>"},{"pid":"5d9590bffd4df3c56cf12965cc5dca3299ff7aad","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T21:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cb266b2b6adb583858edf98a54a7b7577c78bf","tid":312853,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T21:46:34.000Z","msg":"邊個嘅錯先？<br />\n共產黨、地產商、港豬、父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d786d13efdce0040c73a2bc20174925ae31629e1","tid":312853,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T00:20:12.000Z","msg":"咁嘅垃圾樓都要兩萬幾一尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7ad609b28fc6ec40c159308e307cad281589c6","tid":312853,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T00:23:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc6f0a87fd92b400d96e2ecf949d57cab728a06f","tid":312853,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T00:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個嘅錯先？<br />\n共產黨、地產商、港豬、父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人多，屋需求多咗，地有限，自然貴。邊個搞到香港咁撚多人咪邊個錯"},{"pid":"3245d5d5ea65704bb461e3590e7b13c07baf3f20","tid":312853,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T00:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊個嘅錯先？<br />\n共產黨、地產商、港豬、父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人多，屋需求多咗，地有限，自然貴。邊個搞到香港咁撚多人咪邊個錯</blockquote><br />\n新新加坡好似好好多"},{"pid":"57689af620534fc783656a210263f65c15ebeeb5","tid":312853,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T01:01:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個嘅錯先？<br />\n共產黨、地產商、港豬、父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人多，屋需求多咗，地有限，自然貴。邊個搞到香港咁撚多人咪邊個錯</blockquote><br />\n新新加坡好似好好多</blockquote><br />\n新加坡雖然父權主義，但絕少貪官，政策以民為本，唔會亂咁放移民入國搞亂自己國家。睇返香港嗰班垃圾官同新蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005efa4c577a2ef341c00b1728f17045b30a3bba","tid":312853,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個嘅錯先？<br />\n共產黨、地產商、港豬、父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人多，屋需求多咗，地有限，自然貴。邊個搞到香港咁撚多人咪邊個錯</blockquote><br />\n新新加坡好似好好多</blockquote><br />\n新加坡雖然父權主義，但絕少貪官，政策以民為本，唔會亂咁放移民入國搞亂自己國家。睇返香港嗰班垃圾官同新蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為講中文同英文既差別.<br />\n重有香港果班當權者既 DNA 入面奴才媚上既原因."},{"pid":"b3617f4ffefbbb7cb8279a6a4beeb7ae6fe10bd1","tid":312853,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T01:49:17.000Z","msg":"奶波魔召喚"},{"pid":"719d69acca5761172c6dbc1c1e434b8b2d881ebf","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bd2345102b8aaf20ced6185a2318bce56e6188","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efb6dfdd564b37cb6ce8a359cf5726b4405ec7d","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac12e5fad9e26a24faaaa96a0cfd6bccb523fc6b","tid":312853,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊個嘅錯先？<br />\n共產黨、地產商、港豬、父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人多，屋需求多咗，地有限，自然貴。邊個搞到香港咁撚多人咪邊個錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉載自Wiki:<br />\n<br />\n自《中英聯合聲明》簽訂後，鄧小平承諾香港五十年不變，香港前景明朗化，經濟穩步上揚。但另一方面，<span style=\"color: red;\">《中英聯合聲明》限制了香港每年賣地數量</span>，以免殖民地政府在主權移交前把香港最重要的土地資源賣光，然後把財政儲備帶走。在這樣的背景下，香港對房地產的需求因經濟持續上揚而有增無減，但是香港土地供應未有能夠增加，造成1990年代的泡沫經濟，地產、股市都屢創新高，香港經濟一片繁榮，很多人透過炒賣股票和地產而致富，金融業和地產業成為香港經濟重要支柱。據統計，香港的整體樓價在1994年1月至1997年10月的高峰期，3年零10個月之間上升了68%。"},{"pid":"2ffae766a4c2728a43cb20905777359ad1fb18a8","tid":312853,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"每年咁撚多雙非蝗蟲，支那大學生，土匪黨地下黨員，假結婚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港真係會造地都唔撚夠啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任何一個支那人想來就來！"},{"pid":"e7369d34de2e105c104fe12e7996ee31612bf7b7","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b86bbdcdf23ea437c1bc4031d9af605a38adb1","tid":312853,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"267e23e263ff028ab9a631c4cd00e5f7f3338c68","tid":312853,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"係d人話宜家先有納米樓"},{"pid":"6d16dd5ddf77849cb72724aea3e6073685d0a4c6","tid":312853,"uid":93640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家係中產標配，港蟲🐛好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n標你老母配你老豆<br />\n<br />\n死返大陸啦蝗"},{"pid":"7f6cf2cc81faf5a40018a6f8ac42f5733dc4f392","tid":312853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae17e1b3fc08efa021651d46154241893fba604","tid":312853,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係d人話宜家先有納米樓</blockquote><br />\n早於80年代，出現過唔少「牙籤樓」；灣仔、油尖旺、何文田一帶都有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}